Christmas is just around the corner, and we've made it easier to bring offers to your phone by making updates to our push notifications. Happy humming!
With this release, humm will be on Santas Nice list for sure! We’ve made some updates to keep your login even more secure. Happy humming!
We've made it simpler to sign up to humm by enhancing the scan functionality. Just in time for Christmas! Happy humming!
Updates to humm VIP. As a humm VIP you can shop Little Things with no upfront payment.

In these uncertain times we’d love to know what is most important to you. You can now leave feedback for us in the app - keep an eye out for prompt to leave us a review or some feedback. We’re listening.
Happy humming!
